sxNtpx-iT6cw/1QLnbRUqK5MnYPXopLdUY8nY78qNMsau/8" target="_blank"&gt;对中国的关税有了重大削减&lt;/a&gt;，比&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/_iBlePFfkfqDRZfviOi0HaO_R6paDGRZw_C7y3LFjKbSomod_SQk2O7qB_3FvWVrlJmYgaklTf7qf2IYXz1qNkJUDkPdOaitLozBIKM2EexBGuDjQGBliHNDMgvH62fbiaaRdaYRhA3M_kOx4KktYSkyyEP_EIsGZn3NFgCkHxx0T4-AhmKjgJ0mxOAdFQu1o_fMIlM204DV3x3tSnQIYk3LElM0FrWAEpSW-YbXS8VV6LG1gCFB2PV655G9ujLJxudVfAoo_ArfGIuQzB4qAx9VLw/FWe9uKSyRl7RCx4s9wGL-lBxoJtHhMXZ/8" target="_blank"&gt;目前至少145％的水平&lt;/a&gt;低于60％ - 与降级紧张局势进行了交谈。自唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）今年上任以来，包括财政部长斯科特·贝森（Scott Bessent）在内的美国和中国谈判人员&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/J3aXG8BmwEkO9jIP7tcD6kaux1ttAdL0WcIMOT5FuBkDHBtPfE_ZwROQpE-_300tHh-T3HuT9iH_E6vhCIkH-mtjaXSNMvSznPDOXW-gIIvpURjSGLXrebGqZWtf32YeoEZ8xXeSRNtwpzCf8s1qi-iv28_sFMrKvDpbNMuWEZfOGpxLj3kYqD-mi4GWCXbJqOhWDArDmYdhK-AOrr1v35HPyHKkpJyS0ZtW9KGrQLIQfPLbSnSv1cLbwaRgT3yootFp1T6ll7m02YPJAz0L8AjrNA/ZIvQXHL4Tkj7ZEgkMAV6IUXQ-IKmz3Ho/8" target="_blank"&gt;将在瑞士开会&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;说到中国，&lt;/strong&gt;尽管向美国货运下降了21％，但四月份的出口&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/SjxRDhpeEHw-JJfXQXh0Ny5atlfKC47WZVUE_BYZq2HRUGNEPIMYKwr18sx5twaeDhVoM0w4k8GI_bl8xCElUOMZY1bT4TAeDFReIlFQcU-PcYi0HJ0M6ChnM83XxzSaECHt0sPyx8wXsqz8jd4BtpfFWyTk1x1J5i7s3uVaUWcbloaJQK_ahJOKhhcQa6b-4mhSzo_5ctAxbAaqRwHVCnUnfbEDhALtp8HL_2DH2KZI3o93itacIrziKzj3QKQRrV-D_sp7jva4veR7UNtBUVAjjg/SFfT0ki5GwUPOf6bIOSie-78MNXNxW42/8" target="_blank"&gt;增长超出了预期&lt;/a&gt;。来自美国的进口也下降了，但经济学家警告说，从本月起， &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/s5xYe-HSSaqtJtsiEOoQpL4-gyDQtn7i9_BKWwLxJ9km1nUrnV7ysg2kAndLVCigzio9Z42pB4gl-FIAJ39x4EzjlX_E-VCBm368lyc7eAJaufllRMKeRpj3bC0KEp9MwY7RwuS2Yq5HFefqYbz1IGQxoNrtlymydhDxLPOigV_f_6eyTdLvDYddinRNujMKZLemSnUSm7vtKvp3Zi2w_0aavcC4q42tZv7iDBu4mqMtrKnn9ierbFAh9B5WvStsDYP_3OatSKVbD-uuXohGJkDiwg/KmzZl4o12j1ZRNaYDoNj1bq_mJ-fPFnT/8" target="_blank"&gt;关税的影响&lt;/a&gt;可能更为明显。为了减轻其自身经济的打击，中国几周前&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/XQFGYeeV32LS5MCPBVvAbRcu2LG1kEbnpBseOy_p0cm_MHoh7MrbjT9eSikUyG7ZX-90XbdPYyVRzUSga4-UTrVp9Q_1PHb-LvbhKY9YJ0JtqpcqSoC4fa51SSPagm_pOmoHqqfldRImvsSS2Sm0cgprmh0cketJIicen3uyoZ9vgMWzf4V41RS88WBmxGPY8ZfNkw7cFYbAYUhRVRi9K78AWJ4lqIQR-1QMNEdt7UI2pIS6VCM0uD_uUPr9cG8BJqbbGfQ_oTMIIUz06h_rWfUQKA/Yp0pEI3wP8vR2odTAs6ToERr8XhflLHO/8" target="_blank"&gt;开始悄悄地免除&lt;/a&gt;一些美国商品的关税。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;呼吁和平。&lt;/strong&gt;唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump） &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/cayjscSJm-viUzs5bhlyvgQcEmQCYLnIU5zas79qxVszhbtbzOhv40yZfFrpM6ixh9BytDqgd2q9IbGJ_-AZc6BLqg5Mf_ro4evB5n91-WP7hSq0eKDDivlPsnr5KTbfgjPJ_bKOzcixasY_s5kBW1f3TXaxBs5VenGoPow8kJyiOkbZTycMSHa9subQXYuuN7JIv1Az3yKJEyIu3-ls36hFu2ltgQcktlCoi2b_y3KukrCkKjXIb9J01coLZveyynbgIhbcYqUDWdANB36LF9N-dg/EksRSCv-QIEjYSWqcZ0e97f1g1ENWkHt/8" target="_blank"&gt;呼吁与俄罗斯和乌克兰之间的30天停火&lt;/a&gt;，这&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/2KJ-TRwj5-HCsI-b4dTqkXwtCrpPshotyGM7ANZiS6GVGdzgwrzorzTI-XaZ-UvR2uCYelCy78t1pczjWFSr3WuNdsYmq0QYyCUn2v8xzIULeLb4XBjIAt64s76Ei27S4IZlfD8868HRqPbFt9xR9iyY5vBM9jBT6KYdZTtUNAaIO319C4O9TEN3JnXzBinOcfN6B-iacxOQWHISmV3HcH_kPRLW6SraaW_7-WOmR6ESYQGAf530qo5y__jF41rntrCnExhFZUUg7gRWi1RhXk2wYQ/XwJ5Rqyeihf9DblIj-yfF6-Xar_uXvc7/8" target="_blank"&gt;显然与他的副总统JD Vance矛盾&lt;/a&gt;，后者周三表示，美国试图以这样的暂停方式“超越迷恋”。特朗普还威胁说，如果违反休战， &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/Rdrk7lakGTci6P8lKPQ6W5g8HmkQv2WSETJwdoYD819YvsgpF9U2H-xobzz3s-YKeTaef5D_4mkw8QazhY0Kc_Dp9KVryzS-eh0heJT3cowlbih0m2ZIDrkFmRxxF2V-w_j1eiLtMmdVdqwErilyC3IBjwC1BZIQkZaYCwR5R50xQh63CCK4aq7zQQv-f6QmjFqB1UzY9f9RsvvJwa6Sc-eePUojcGuSrP4paDqh7samm6iyQbxQ24Y8pQALhb6u3h14im7gBHbkl07eaRMiPbpL9g/SBnsAqNZEp2TELCZ_vo7k17bwnBdhY8P/8" target="_blank"&gt;他的政府一直在为休战做出了进一步的制裁。&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="body-image" style="margin: 20px 0px;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/o2D19_JMmVc1A5_mvWUCEsY9lHkFspAkhM0lHioeYnfQoMcO5vrSoZm8C4Xb6b0yKDkgDu9Y-q29JdGmokapLj_1RQ5BNqzAQ5LwEaFV_yUTfsbwfxxRqdscOEC4CllZJCTI2yJobupsdztosMy7nLRBOr2c3CeDk9N2wlG66ZUpaay-cF7vjWnFP6lxiZlD-Bzls2v6Eeu8hBwxXDlCsJbcxN6kf7hgJi7KeDXLbjKhG-beSUndaA-4EwrlgOtJz7SDOmr0Er_i6FQAhD3nswsUnA/-pGtLWRGDnkXlSwVH3xOnnC2mIg8TlyN/8" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="550"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/itNnUcD4PCiY/v0/-1x-1.jpg" width="550"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="alt" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/itNnUcD4PCiY/v0/-1x-1.jpg" style="display: block; width: 530px; margin: auto;" width="530" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;div style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 130%; margin-top: 8px;"&gt; Jeanine Pirro于2024年5月30日在曼哈顿刑事法院外部&lt;i&gt;。摄影师：James Devaney/GC Images/Getty Images&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;特朗普聘请了福克斯新闻主持人&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;珍妮·皮罗（Jeanine Pirro）在国会反对派中&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/fi5vWlSU5n2FjSGk-NVesvJiFBzvg8NX_GuIteY0sAfKxsXjv5j8IeeBvIETBez3qRPkIU2fQ0ynL59p3w9_zdRSyejz5gVNBBgpscv3hrEElCRvFwpf6a_uBgyMRpWEGO8JROux_S6E9qzkvIw7paOCE8-HEojvRwgIHUS34-bCvrDd4koHgC-8-HaJnbbMI37EEzBRjH8P5XF3iQfAE9bp0fy2D5Zn3w-dXsCSeP3IrbhOCweNo6zgOggtNi7dvSSDrsKVmxb1w-yKdNjj2CwqTg/Lg0HkpNHxWp77cVKMVFp22yFBjgqybGq/8" target="_blank"&gt;提名埃德&lt;/a&gt;·马丁（Ed Martin）后， &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/RZPstcSJ1eP0uinckzB-046kXEUPiFhfKQybELefsUlFhW36od7PeA07eY5jvzxBPPlDHFMUTdZarPT43fXXxxSFrpn5B5c332VWhq_41Dz0RZAdvyYZrJYckGYzjJASPiu-Iwxz1kBS-SvntooyP0Yx84Q6yAV7tQOrnfxAVMS8ZFQkHolgUL9CY0