中国对美国的出口量&lt;/a&gt;下跌。数据仅捕获关税的最初损害，其影响可能从本月开始变得更加明显。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;德国的达克斯（Dax）成为第一个超过&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/45QvZSkZrjknbStdJReHE5KCc7SrctfvO9kHih37jyfTvTY6t0yHirXRJTqQK9V5IlA9wPhpLFh9xJXX6VM12S2KhWq9Of2Db7dXkiAFlxYN2qm9GhewKBaUWca71NvmxIk7ru09I-Sgbr9HyZ3eQoZy1gz-3_GpJSoqoK8wp2eMSvxbypC_ytusPfWOh9IZkoMz3c95_UiLKf_Eb75pd_NLmn3wKOv8iDE5mAGv5tmOfsM-NKPH1Jdu31GqiVJlAuKaVpBV6NWu2nrpQAiueBzBUg/B3N4YJ_jWo-QJ2ZoTdFY7Yov9c3kQmaz/8" target="_blank" title="关联"&gt;3月份纪录高的&lt;/a&gt;欧洲主要股票指数，这使特朗普的贸易战争引起了所有衰落。欧洲的股票正在&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/GFrIpXRoIj-OMxr5MUG2qDl7UF_GtVWMoopBQy-AyMFWqxMnvhGXPrFahSCXtpDDkFSVoV_juG3yy4OsvYgEHorw9iFFwVsqxZfKCLQ1pj16AZ67egO4yl-TDYJKaNoqkiZ_QPac2142qF48oDFLSiLeavJOrrnpLUDGjBD3fBRu1hX55yhUBeSkrvJ2-igZa4t6ps1_tBY56c_ILKSZOad8yjCfvwUq6ugTi-9aEqktaHKc9U85edRc-XXNF7CWIsIEAZn8HvV_fraWtPEASVhCHw/LgQRPexyv8bwE-EVtjmjEYW1nwwof_L9/8" target="_blank" title="关联"&gt;减轻关税紧张局势&lt;/a&gt;，并提出欧洲央行政策制定者的建议，即下个月可能会削减利率。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;特朗普正在推动立法者&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/zj_23iztHw6PfkuJpZJ1qXprKiD9lu5yrGyBHr1QVr3CV3QXCRIgmghvBNP29BvBJF_Rg2j1zJfYulYUgyNGC-HiN4nKqNtN4sGwdoG63mVsD5MBsktAnX2BoL_t3Zir206SbHJix-tee5mbso1hSDSS4jrhPQz5h1gzM3pehY86fx-nQ8qi5uqvxSiZprbqHiCm4JiytBRUES_y_XlS_rnrDNymZLr6ySDWqy8Ys7Xx-rjTwlHn9nb84QCR-2XWJPeule0BRqsmVCEGb8NOxIL7Og/P-FIKoTA9lEdOt7QrDmTuCUasukirR61/8" target="_blank" title="关联"&gt;对富人提高税收&lt;/a&gt;。熟悉讨论的人说，他呼吁为赚取至少250万美元的个人或赚取500万美元的夫妇提供新的39.6％的税率。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt; Panasonic计划裁员&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/zhbTya8g2XXmUeGRCJqxsDqNX9wOT7-5q337KCQAyjnJ0sKIGK-T8GNbKX2Tvo-4i_U5Z3T_hf-Tuf6vyBJDyQCC3mW1SgLGy0KINcB9vw77PJUkYa3pxp_to8YmkCJIcf2H7o0FToCeuQ4HlQONVImtWeV9NP79_-UQtGw8avFAwVFFqKxjRGiHCP26fRc3MGT8IgoiAJuk92LxFW3RfHt0DhNHUqsvQQKAfxaDcxmHCr-l2dvFMPsE0g24df0wZlV7mjBHf32YglelWDw5kbvu3w/dR6buFn7afJKMqia18eJHlenWKiTLjpG/8" target="_blank" title="关联"&gt;10,000个工作岗位，&lt;/a&gt;以此作为提高盈利能力的推动力。这家为特斯拉提供电池的日本公司旨在简化未生长的运营和修剪区域，例如工业设备和电视。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;em&gt;在&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/OEZPrlZL4Esn0hNZfjqTS1j0dah108X3-gpYFNhXDWJ8llCFiV7ykyXVFStFOC8IyVU9LXw-K8x0xNlbXqmCBQTOfg1hwsoIiiYvPA49r64wRXEs5N5w6O17fzhv7CbncV6hfYIt6aU0oV9CZNN8gjygNbxqsS4HN1ah_6f4xtairjUqeZAKjxe0qqfqRPYF4XXp93LY0V29Ry6UsENjLMGWeZsy_vaqgH3SmDen2yZo9kZ__0dTPeG-exZmOWHHlgR56JVA37anYAT7BmMiYHgOWg/dmeJJRMis8pFLl1YxwYuL0E2zHGOjtmj/8" target="_blank" title="关联"&gt;特朗普学&lt;/a&gt;的新情节中：尼尔·弗格森（Niall Ferguson）和菲德·扎卡里亚（Fareed Zakaria）加入了唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）在历史角度将唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）为美国经济的雄心勃勃的计划。在&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/h-eFfzGLFpIjbIqDiFMQ7hs1ps7NreZmi11epZu2HIn-wX1P5HtPCOnbFL2zkxHMyNMoHSqUtcOd2VX0vFWV40ja1wkK-fB0Xg3vujqiYyGqHAHjp-RWWfj_KkiqI3bTBGB0I2Wc-7FnNvDrJWTj5Hwxd8kbRnlfGPk7AYfr4Co1IqZcr5l6ZzNc6J4WcKzVgdBO_gdf4Iz22v3Dih5cOzJTYaXTezQKGuO1T2q269FM0bJ_PAyY-0a1f1SBhWIaSTj54KARXujbemYV6HLeaIRyEH1eHhyEUSn3F3x7R_2QV7O2eCw2q7QEqRYuKfcLKr5X13vzTajKQeXEnEU5z8AJKPvzp2AK-BL-ER5RbNxnnJnisPNC97HCweVozjrGOQynxIU8-z3-3l0vOQ6S/e6TonVG15I_qnsqc_BXkwoApc6OAvu8t/8"&gt;Apple&lt;/a&gt; ， &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/0iYBc3T97lPC7mUtPX58Af1JLAah3WmNEsFZNUWudFGiRY4f7XHdOrsLsqOCTWD5MJ5H6HhLwkXhHGX78fjB7MqQyojF679Z9nu7FvkFD7aNoAVHp_yFgFVtAGBhd3C7kFsSO9VGKopzgt16JigKEnJgAMIrMLYk06EjC3olwoYjQRcZ_B2FxKKTGK00L1WBZmxoX__l8b8rFvWE2f2AdFN5jSjBIwgedP0mdevbYHkAFXDoufdITexLqm2MQsnyuMNzthSQbjtSHTWUWlSNfCDtlX6FqOsdr2GPT6ePmxih4z9WStr2rXqSmrhQ9UOaspzg6dhFniYFt0tl-xnZ1AL9FdsGhnmy/EBQkgL79OOqLfMc7ApqVk-0fUfymF_T4/8"&gt;Spotify&lt;/a&gt;或任何获得播客的地方收听。&lt;/em&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;table align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="auto"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td align="center" colspan="